Description: # SlothStock
        
        [![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/slothstock.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/slothstock)
        [![PyPI license](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/slothstock.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/slothstock/)
